overview: Chris Steele's Big Dick Society II: Dicktimized is a sequel to the 2008 smash hit Chris Steele's Big Dick Society, which was the second highest grossing movie Jet Set released in 2008. Dicktimized also features the return of the infamous Size-O-Matic, a machine that measures the size of a guy's dick and, if big enough, gives him the green light (and an accepting ring of the bell) to enter the world of the Big Dick Society. If he doesn't measure up, he gets the red light and the ding of the buzzer.
title: Big Dick Society 2: Dicktimized
